       https://github.com/InfraTales
       https://infratales.com"

2. NO REMOVAL OF BRANDING
   The following elements MUST NOT be removed or altered:
   
   a) InfraTales branding in code comments and headers
   b) Author attribution (Rahul Ladumor)
   c) Original repository links
   d) Copyright notices
   e) Any embedded signatures or watermarks

3. DERIVATIVE WORKS
   Any derivative work or fork MUST:
   
   a) Clearly state it is derived from InfraTales
   b) Link to the original InfraTales repository
   c) Not imply original authorship or ownership
   d) Include "Based on InfraTales by Rahul Ladumor" prominently

4. COMMERCIAL USE
   Commercial use is permitted PROVIDED THAT:
   
   a) All attribution requirements above are met
   b) InfraTales branding is not removed
   c) The work is not sold as if it were original work
   d) Credit is given in any commercial documentation

